## AutoML Series ü§ñ
The AutoML series explores various **open source AutoML libraries** covering the following topics (wherever applicable):

* Installation and setup
* Data preparation and validation
* Model hyper-parameters and their usage
* Interpreting single and ensemble models
* *Experiment tracking with MLFlow and Aim [WIP]*
* Extracting outputs and verifying results
* Baseline examples on Kaggle TPS Competitions
